						<div class="postbody">Hi, from the famitone2 readme:<br />- No volume column support <br />- Only Volume, Arpeggio, and Pitch sequences (no Pitch for noise channel) supported<br />I understand the 1st row, but don't understand the 2nd row.  <img src="./images/smilies/icon_redface.gif" alt=":oops:" title="Embarassed" /> <br />Can I change the volume of a channel? (and if yes, how?)</div>

