						<div class="postbody">I agree that the volume column is very important.<br /><br />At some point, though, the question becomes &quot;why not use the full famitracker driver&quot;? Shiru's version.<br /><br />I think ir might be because it hasn't been rewritten for their preferred assembler yet.<br /><br />Size is another problem. Adding a volume column adds a byte per volume change. That could amount to 1000 extra bytes (3 channels * 20 per section *10 sections per song *4 songs = 2400 bytes).</div>

					
